Sprint, Falcone’s LightSquared Agree to 15-Year Network Accord

-- B y   D e v i n   B a n e r j e e
-- 
2011-07-28T10:30:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/sprint-falcone-s-lightsquared-agree-to-15-year-network-expansion-accord.html
Billionaire  Philip Falcone ’s
LightSquared Inc. struck a 15-year deal with  Sprint Nextel
Corp. (S)  to share network expansion costs and equipment in an
effort aimed at making both stronger wireless competitors.  To contact the reporter on this story:
